	<tr>
		
			<td colspan="2" bgcolor="#DEDACB" background="http://www.everlore.com/gimages/tb_beige.gif">
		
				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Just spent 6 weeks camping this guy. Here is what I know.  The spawn time is about 3 hours &amp; 15 minutes.  The live (human) version spawns during the day (EQ time) &amp; the dead (skeleton) spawns at night (EQ time).  The placeholder for him is a putrid skeleton.  The PH spawned about 80% of the time for me.  EQ time is about 1 hour every 3 minutes real time.  So with a 3 hour 15 min (approximately) spawn time to get the live version kill the ph around 6pm EQ time &amp; to get the dead one kill the ph around 6am EQ time.  This time line was worked great for me once I got it down.  Hope this helps.
				</font>
			</td>

	</tr>
	
