				<font face="verdana" size="2" color="black">
				Alright, i completed this quest today, the live version of grimrot is very difficult for a lvl 47 cleric to solo, so i had some help from a 47 shadowknight guildie, and i only healed her once.  I have made him spawn twice, but the first time he was stolen from me, so ill tell you how to make the live one spawn, I dont know exactly how to make the dead one spawn, i hear you kill the standing putrid skeleton at 8pm game time and wait 3 real hours.  But for the live version, kill the standing putrid skeleton under the hut with no hat at exactly 10pm, and 3 hours later, Lord Grimrot will spawn.  just to add a little more, i killed the place holder 3 times at 10pm and he spawned 2 of those times, the 1 time he didnt spawn was when another cleric went rampaging through the undead camp and kill all the skeletons. so ive come to the conclusion that you should kill the placeholder and try to keep anything else in the camp from dying.  laterz
				</font>
